title.rendered: ARTICLE: Calgary housing market: What’s behind ‘exceptionally strong’ sales? [CANADIAN MORTGAGE PROFESSIONAL, MAY 2022]

content.rendered:
As other regions’ sales plummeted year over year, Alberta’s largest city posted robust annual growth. Canadian Mortgage Professional met with Kim Nguyen, Vine Group Mortgage Associate and Regional Team Lead, and discussed the growing interest in Alberta real estate from out-of-province buyers.

Full article linked here.
